'''Pride Month 2025''' is a community event to celebrate [[Wikipedia:Pride Month|Pride Month]] for 2025. The event featured a pride-themed hub world, a charity fundraising campaign for Trans Lifeline, and several rewards for users participating. It took place from June 11, 2025 - June 30, 2025.

==Details==
On May 28, 2025, VRChat shared a post<ref>"Celebrate #VRCPride2025 with us this year!", https://x.com/VRChat/status/1927883086261350413.</ref> on their social media outlining their plans for the Pride Month 2025 event. Attached to the post was a [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yG6h2G8Di7k video] and a link to the [https://hello.vrchat.com/pride-2025 Pride 2025 landing page].

The landing page includes notable dates of the timeline of the event:

* June 11: Charity Hub World & Fundraising Begins
* June 20: The Official VRChat Pride Parade Stream
* June 30: Exclusive Pride Content Rewards

==Hub world==
''See also [[VRChat Official Pride Hub]] for more detailed information.''

The VRChat Official Pride Hub is where users can come together and celebrate LGBTQIA+ community during the event. The hub features, posters, pride floats and representable flags, set in a vibrant nighttime island.

==Pride campaign==
[[File:VRChat Pride Month 2025 event campaign finished screenshot.png|thumb|Finished Pride Campaign 2025 menu screenshot]]
The Pride Campaign is a charity fundraising campaign for Trans Lifeline, a trans-led nonprofit that offers direct emotional and financial support to trans people in crisis.<ref>"Pride 2025 — VRChat", https://hello.vrchat.com/pride-2025.</ref> VRChat will match all Gift Drop purchases, and 20% of [[VRC+]] gift purchases, donating up to $100,000USD.

Users can participate and track progress by navigating to the Pride Campaign tab in the VRC+ page, or through the campaign boards in the hub world or the [[VRChat Home]]. By participating in the campaign, users earned several rewards.

On June 13, VRChat announced that they will be doubling their match for Trans Lifeline from $50K to $100K, due to overwhelming support<ref> "VRChat is doubling our match for Trans Lifeline from $50K to $100K!", https://x.com/VRChat/status/1933634517849321770.</ref>. The goal was reached on June 20<ref> "We raised $100k to donate to Trans Lifeline!", https://x.com/VRChat/status/1936086232980676968.</ref>. 

The final participation stats for $100,000 goal are: 
* 24,680 total participants
* 36,819 total VRC+ gifts and gift drops.

'''Note:''' These stats are when the campaign met it's $100,000 goal, users who participated after the goal was met are not included in the total.

The campaign began at 4:58PM UTC on June 11th and ended at 11:59:59PM UTC on June 30th. 

===Rewards===
Users that participated during the pride campaign are subject to the following rewards:

* Pride Welcome Bundle
** Available to everyone
** "Rainbow" [[Stickers|sticker]] & [[Emojis|emoji]]

* Pride Badge
** Available to users who gifted at least once
** "Pride Supporter" [[Badges|badge]]

* Pride 2025 Community Gift Drop
** Available to users who gifted at least once
** "Party Rat", "Unity", "Rat Rainbow", "Butterfly", "DJ Cat", "Pride Kitty", and "Love Wins" stickers

* Mystery Gift
** Available to everyone
** "Rainbow Ribbon" [[Items|item]]

